music.prompt:
[Verse]
Seven shadows on the wall
Whispers rise but never fall
What’s the sound behind the door

[Prechorus]
Do you feel it crawling near
Is it hope or just your fear

[Chorus]
Questions float like smoke in air
Answers vanish—do we care
Mystery
Mystery everywhere

[Verse 2]
A clock that ticks but skips the time
A bell that rings without a chime
Who’s the voice that speaks in rhyme

[Bridge]
Turn the key but it won’t fit
Truth and lies
A perfect split
Every answer’s counterfeit

[Chorus]
Questions float like smoke in air
Answers vanish—do we care
Mystery
Mystery everywhere
music.title: Mystery in the Air

music.prompt:
[Verse]
Who am I in the mirror’s haze
Why does the sky shift a hundred ways
Where do the stars go when they fall
Is this my life or is it all

[Prechorus]
What’s the sound of silence breaking
Why’s my heart always aching aching

[Chorus]
Why why why does it feel so wrong
Why why why can’t I belong
Is there a place where I fit in
Or am I chasing the wind

[Verse 2]
What’s the cost of a dream too big
Can you plant a seed on a stone so thick
Do the waves hear the moon’s soft call
Or do they crash with no thought at all

[Bridge]
Why do we run when the road’s not straight
Why do we fight when it’s just too late
Questions questions pile up high
But the answers always pass me by

[Chorus]
Why why why does it feel so wrong
Why why why can’t I belong
Is there a place where I fit in
Or am I chasing the wind
music.title: The Question Song
music.tags: pop, electronic with pulsing synths and tight drum loops

music.prompt:
